column5: Was a great day Perchin on Simcoe,out at 8:30,(I know it was late) back in at 2:30,was an awesome day out there,anywhere from 8" to 14"in. 17 to 22 fow. Can't wait to get out tomorrow again. Muckluk,get up on time tomorrow!!
Great to hear you got out Al... not own a camera! LOL
So we are a lot alike....
now the fish that finds the camera can take pictures of the other 4 fish that are wearing my glasses!!
